data.description: A GREAT OPPORTUNITY to own a Charming Monticello Townhome!! This 2 bedroom, 2 bath END UNIT has only one shared wall and is located in the interior of the community. A spacious living room with cathedral ceilings connects to the kitchen with eating area.  The main floor bedroom has sliding glass doors that provide tons of light, large closets and a guest bath.  Upstairs the primary bedroom with ensuite bath includes large closets and french doors. An enclosed breezeway with skylights offers flex space for an office or an additional sitting area. Fresh paint throughout and new carpet.   2 car attached garage with laundry area. Residents receive one parking permit for first come/first serve parking and access to a guest parking lot. Close to restaurants, schools, park, OC Fairgrounds, beaches and the Back Bay.  Convenient freeway access.  This home has room to update and add your personal touch.  Lots of potential! A must see!!
